WEBVTT

00:01.040 --> 00:03.840
This has been my new favorite late night snack lately.

00:03.841 --> 00:05.121
Let me show you what I do.

00:05.122 --> 00:09.181
I grab a bowl, I add some sliced up strawberries to it.

00:10.680 --> 00:13.120
Also add some whole milk to it.

00:13.121 --> 00:15.341
You can use whatever milk you want.

00:19.600 --> 00:21.520
I like to add quite a lot.

00:21.521 --> 00:25.441
And then sometimes I like to add just a little bit of sugar to it.

00:25.442 --> 00:27.121
But you can leave this out.

00:27.122 --> 00:29.941
Some nights I do. I sprinkle that on top.

00:31.760 --> 00:33.920
This is the perfect sweet treat.

00:33.921 --> 00:35.321
It tastes so good.

00:35.322 --> 00:39.101
There's something about the combination of strawberries and milk.

00:39.600 --> 00:42.780
Divine. This is what we're working with.

00:43.280 --> 00:45.840
Used to have this all the time when I was small.

00:45.841 --> 00:48.161
It's basically just strawberries and milk,

00:48.162 --> 00:50.901
but this combination is so good.

00:52.560 --> 00:55.480
It reminds me of strawberries and cream,

00:55.481 --> 00:57.001
which I also really like having.

00:57.002 --> 01:00.461
But there's something so simple about the milk with the strawberry
